                        <p><hi rend="smallcaps">Notes.</hi>—In the coinage of the fiscal year there
                            are wanting reports for five months from the mints of Alamos, Oaxaca,
                            Culiacan, and Hemosillo. To supply them an average is taken of the
                            coinage for the year.</p>
                        <p>In the fiscal year 1878 to 1879 the coinage of the first six months only
                            is given, as the reports from all the mints are not yet received.</p>
